thread/266137/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/GWRhF0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FGWRhF0.jpg&h=0bada67c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/fNzoyM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FfNzoyM.jpg&h=ecaa1dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/g9n5Mw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fg9n5Mw.jpg&h=b627d395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/CnDakq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FCnDakq.jpg&h=6e4b42ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/oGw89R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FoGw89R.jpg&h=1dc3dd07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ecf021e9409e10fa726cfa7ae4c0518ee91cf1a","tid":321471,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:00:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9cddf208499b88bf518d12dbea98d3f7a9415f6e","tid":321471,"uid":99872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:00:15.000Z","msg":"呢d仆街係度挑撥離間，邊個唔比梁天琦入閘架？發生左梁游件事未？成件事來來去去都係共匪賤到出汁，你地係度離間，其實你地咁做為物？$0.5？"},{"pid":"70d38d489da8111a6a54f9650c1dc1b781867162","tid":321471,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:01:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前都驚block錯 而家可以confirm了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我講事實，唔好係我啲post出現就最好。"},{"pid":"911323bdf8d0cf001cc64a1f5762d794088c4d7b","tid":321471,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:02:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d仆街係度挑撥離間，邊個唔比梁天琦入閘架？發生左梁游件事未？成件事來來去去都係共匪賤到出汁，你地係度離間，其實你地咁做為物？$0.5？</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好扯咁遠，我淨係針對「忽略宣誓」。</span></span>"},{"pid":"9979630377c268227f5ea1ddab93220a6485d334","tid":32