x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將議會比喻做建制</span></span><br />\n笑撚死人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">笑撚死我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n議會就係建制嘅一部分！基本法都有寫明係。<br />\n<br />\n唔識字嘅五毛，所以咪要做五毛搵食囉！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n用寵物小精靈嘅支那譯名係唔係五毛？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正常香港人一定知道係「寵物小精靈」，但係支那移民，五毛唔知道，當然唔出奇。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n用殘體轉正體字電腦程式<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/305831/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/305831/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vzxl9rh0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvzxl9rh0&h=ed5dd348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2016/02/20160226_ll_136_6/gamersky_03small_06_2016226145065D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2016%2F02%2F20160226_ll_136_6%2Fgamersky_03small_06_2016226145065D.jpg&h=884648fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a181cd7db3d06187be6d7e20dd26a830f33f872","tid":321471,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:48:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf4f12975344b7ab24d46bf1056a179137948d1c","tid":321471,"uid":34273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:48:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係好似自己覺得開架私家車好簡單，所以揸大膽車，出事死人，唔好話鬼掩眼嚟逃避責任！</blockquote><br />\n大膽車?你係唔係記錯左d野，你自己講忽略宣誓一早就有先例，並唔係違法，只係中共濫用釋法延伸先變到係違法，再加上可以秋後算帳<br />\n即係好似條路明明一直都可以左轉，但當權者突然發難，話左轉就係違法，再將改法前左轉嘅都當違法，責任係邊個到?"},{"pid":"9348144609c1d98b98a56bd5dd81158e22bd2085","tid":321471,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:48:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>五毛又係到玩語言藝術 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將議會比喻做建制</span></span><br />\n笑撚死人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">笑撚死我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n議會就係建制嘅一部分！基本法都有寫明係。<br />\n<br />\n唔識字嘅五毛，所以咪要做五毛搵食囉！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n用寵物小精靈嘅支那譯名係唔係五毛？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正常香港人一定知道係「寵物小精靈」，但係支那移民，五毛唔知道，當然唔出奇。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n用殘體轉正體字電腦程式<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/305831/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/305831/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vzxl9rh0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvzxl9rh0&h=ed5dd348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2016/02/20160226_ll_136_6/gamersky_03small_06_2016226145065D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2016%2F02%2F20160226_ll_136_6%2Fgamersky_03small_06_2016226145065D.jpg&h=884648fa&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4e9787ec1d4e84be179850a3ca6aa399b980238b","tid":321471,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:53:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即係好似自己覺得開架私家車好簡單，所以揸大膽車，出事死人，唔好話鬼掩眼嚟逃避責任！</blockquote><br />\n大膽車?你係唔係記錯左d野，你自己講忽略宣誓一早就有先例，並唔係違法，只係中共濫用釋法延伸先變到係違法，再加上可以秋後算帳<br />\n即係好似條路明明一直都可以左轉，但當權者突然發難，話左轉就係違法，再將改法前左轉嘅都當違法，責任係邊個到?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基本法的確係有明文規定「忽略宣誓」<br />\n<br />\n以前曾鈺成仲有江湖地位，仲可以守得住後面隻無形之手，但係唔代表唔存在。（當時文匯大公都屌鳩黃毓民「忽略宣誓」）<br />\n<br />\n問題係執唔執法問題。到而家執正嚟做，唔睇建制說明書，其實可以話係抵撚死！"},{"pid":"c44c0f3557bfa7792f8bbc0206eba29f7abfaf6b","tid":321471,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:59:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"072ad9a38b00441e9e57ef8973ead6ddd6090b47","tid":321471,"uid":34273,"like":0