 xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁點解黃毓民係2012年要重新宣誓？明明「忽略宣誓」一直存在！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n監誓依個權力就係立法會秘書監誓，立法會主席或任何代其行事的議員監誓，佢哋有權裁定「忽略宣誓」定係無。唔鍾意佢哋嘅裁決咪告去法庭囉。<br />\n<br />\n而家個人大釋法就係規範化咗「宣誓」嘅定義同模式，但係唔代表一直「宣誓」可以自由發揮。只可以話以前捉得唔嚴。"},{"pid":"12509c2e058ea4bc4d78bfab39f42223f04acf2a","tid":321471,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T20:11:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宣誓第一個玩野係長毛</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家梁游玩撚爛咗個遊戲，大家仲唔多謝佢哋兩個天才共諜。</span></span>"},{"pid":"48f4c0532f1d2d153b27de11728f29af9cdd0c8f","tid":321471,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T20:14:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇埋個判詞，好多地方都係引用「梁游玩撚爛咗個遊戲」個案例嚟DQ而家4個泛民。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家仲唔多謝佢哋兩個天才共諜。"},{"pid":"4d3c122c847fba67364b433982f1777b85f4d557","tid":321471,"uid":122601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T03:18:34.000Z","msg":"on99 中共幾時都可以釋法，只不過佢地唔好彩第一個受罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 梁遊唔釋，中共一樣可以等長毛佢地再釋，dq哂6個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家d 人d logic 真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7236db7edcd12bd3cc3bbfc1e9f137935d27ac09","tid":321471,"uid":122968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T03:29:02.000Z","msg":"其實理性d諗 根本係梁游玩大左 比位人入 如果唔係起碼宜家立法會勢力會平均d"},{"pid":"47ed43a026867aaa56baf104435841333ec5cac0","tid":321471,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T03:31:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45d3f98660fd6d052deb3e460eaa0058590d2223","tid":321471,"uid":63635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T03:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}